on for the\nsources detected in the H-ATLAS equatorial fields, finding a bimodal\ndistribution with a mean redshift of 1.2, 1.9 and 2.5 for 250, 350 and 500 um\nselected sources respectively. \\end{abstract}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Aug 2013 20:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
